data.description: Life is great in this Contempo near schools. The contemporary style of this home epitomizes your unique ambiance. 3 bedrooms, 2 and 1/2 baths. Everyday meals do not have to be formal because you have an eat-in kitchen with granite countertops, a built-in microwave, stainless steel appliances, and a center island. There are no washday blues here, thanks to the main-level laundry. Entertain or simply relax on the comfortable enclosed patio with a hot tub. Find many other delightful features in this charmer, such as a family room, fireplace, wood laminate flooring, and a private master suite with a balcony to relax on with your morning coffee. Walk-in closets, garden tub, ceiling fans, two-car garage, covered front porch, and wood fence. Bright and cheery with pleasing amenities!
